snippet.title: 'HOtt PiXX by Vic' Fashion-Model Ratings: Emperial, Amber Easton, Amanda Gift (Pt 1/3)
snippet.description: (www.paxstereo.tv/hottpixx) "HOtt PiXX by Vic" Fashion-Model ratings present individuals various photos and pictures from social networking profiles judged by the Morning Coffee Crew & guest. Featured female models are Emperial Photograhy, Amber Easton and Amanda Gift. Featured male models are Trayll Brandon, John and Steven Montalvo. We rate from 1-10 the best commercial photo from the female and male group. Singer-artist 'Akapello Di General' and Photographer Donald Carraway of Don C. Images and Velvet Ropes Entertainment join's our fashion segment. Come on down! (09-19-11) PART 1 of 2 -- THIS IS A PARTIAL EPISODE
